# Sales Performance Dashboard - Power BI

## Overview
This project analyzes 10,000+ sales records to identify:
- Revenue trends
- Regional performance
- Product profitability
- KPI metrics

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- DAX
- Data Modeling

## Key Insights
- Electronics category contributes highest revenue.
- West region shows highest profit margin.
- Profit margin averages around 20%.

## Dashboard Features
- Revenue & Profit KPIs
- Category-wise performance
- Regional analysis
- Dynamic slicers & filters
